\u00e9MON plays happily if thunder rumbles in the sky."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"It rotates its arms to generate electricity, but it tires easily, so it charges up only a little bit."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It generates electricity by whirling its arms. However, it can\u2019t store the energy it makes."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It generates electricity by whirling its arms. However, it can\u2019t store the energy it makes."},{"version":"platinum","text":"A weak electric current flows between its horns. Sticking a hand there shocks the unwary."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"It rotates its arms to generate electricity, but it tires easily, so it only charges up a little bit."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Even in the most vicious storm, this Pok\u00e9mon plays happily if thunder rumbles in the sky."},{"version":"black","text":"A weak electric current flows between its horns. Sticking a hand there shocks the unwary."},{"version":"white","text":"A weak electric current flows between its horns. Sticking a hand there shocks the unwary."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Spinning its arms around to generate electricity makes the area between its horns shine light blue."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Spinning its arms around to generate electricity makes the area between its horns shine light blue."},{"version":"x","text":"It generates electricity by whirling its arms. However, it can\u2019t store the energy it makes."},{"version":"y","text":"Spinning its arms around to generate electricity makes the area between its horns shine light blue."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Elekid stores electricity in its body. If it touches metal and accidentally discharges all its built-up electricity, this Pok\u00e9mon begins swinging its arms in circles to recharge itself."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Elekid stores electricity in its body. If it touches metal and accidentally discharges all its built-up electricity, this Pok\u00e9mon begins swinging its arms in circles to recharge itself."},{"version":"sun","text":"When it\u2019s in a house, electrical outlets serve as its baby bottles. It sucks down electricity."},{"version":"moon","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon is constantly fighting with Togedemaru that try to steal its electricity. It\u2019s a pretty even match."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"When it hears the crash of thunder, Elekid\u2019s mood improves. It can be useful to record that sound and play it when Elekid\u2019s feeling down."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"When its horns shine a bluish white, that\u2019s the sign it\u2019s fully charged. You\u2019ll get a shocking jolt if you touch it!"},{"version":"sword","text":"When a storm approaches, this Pok\u00e9mon gets restless. Once Elekid hears the sound of thunder, it gets full-on rowdy."},{"version":"shield","text":"It\u2019s not good at storing electricity yet. This Pok\u00e9mon sneaks into people\u2019s homes, looking for electrical outlets to eat electricity from."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"They generate electricity by spinning their arms. During a thunderstorm, if one hears the lively voices of children out in the wilderness, what one is actually hearing are the voices of Elekid."}],"evo":{"name":"elekid","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"electabuzz","level":1,"min_level":30,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"electivire","level":2,"min_level":null,"trigger":"trade","item":null,"held_item":"electirizer","known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":nu